# Inner Animal Media — Cursor

**Platform identity (read before any product work):** `docs/platform/PLATFORM_CONSTITUTION.md` → `docs/workspace/WORKSPACE_CONSTITUTION.md` → `docs/products/PRODUCT_REGISTRY.md`

**Always-on rules:** `.cursor/rules/iam-core.mdc` · `.cursor/rules/iam-ship-gate.mdc` (local → git → full deploy — required for PWA/phone updates) · `.cursor/rules/iam-agent-delivery-workflow.mdc`

**Ship gate:** every deploy must pass local, stage/commit/push, then `npm run deploy:full` — no partial handoffs.

**No test/smoke in deploy** unless you explicitly ask (see iam-core).

**Optional (agent loads when relevant):** other files in `.cursor/rules/` with `alwaysApply: false` — e.g. `iam-gcp-vm-self-heal.mdc` for iam-tunnel git/SSH/pm2 failures.

**Platform law in D1:** `agentsam_rules_document` — query at runtime with `d1_query` / migrations. Do **not** paste table catalogs or schemas into Cursor rules.

**Never commit:** `.cursor/mcp.json` (developer-owned), `.env.cloudflare`, secrets, `*.bak`, `.scratch/`.
